 "productcatalogservice-1", "recommendationservice-2", "shippingservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-02": [], "aiops-k8s-03": ["recommendationservice-1", "shippingservice-2", "frontend-0", "paymentservice-1", "cartservice-0", "adservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["frontend-2", "currencyservice-1", "checkoutservice-0", "paymentservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["paymentservice-2", "currencyservice-0", "cartservice-1", "paymentservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["productcatalogservice-0", "emailservice-2", "checkoutservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["currencyservice-2", "adservice-1", "frontend-1", "emailservice-0", "shippingservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["recommendationservice-0", "paymentservice-0", "productcatalogservice-2", "cartservice-2", "redis-cart-0", "adservice-2"]}, "matched_anomaly": "Please analyze the abnormal event between 2025-06-12T23:10:15Z and 2025-06-12T23:29:15Z and provide the root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-12 23:10:15+00:00 to 2025-06-12 23:29:15+00:00"}, "metric_data_collected": true, "node_pod_mapping": {"aiops-k8s-01": ["checkoutservice-1", "emailservice-1", "productcatalogservice-1", "recommendationservice-2", "shippingservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-02": [], "aiops-k8s-03": ["recommendationservice-1", "shippingservice-2", "frontend-0", "paymentservice-1", "cartservice-0", "adservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["frontend-2", "currencyservice-1", "checkoutservice-0", "paymentservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["paymentservice-2", "currencyservice-0", "cartservice-1", "paymentservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["productcatalogservice-0", "emailservice-2", "checkoutservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["currencyservice-2", "adservice-1", "frontend-1", "emailservice-0", "shippingservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["recommendationservice-0", "paymentservice-0", "productcatalogservice-2", "cartservice-2", "redis-cart-0", "adservice-2"]}, "log_analysis_findings": "### 分析结果\n\n根据提供的日志数据，以下是对故障假设的验证：\n\n#### 假设：\n'Node aiops-k8s-08 memory exhaustion is the root cause, impacting adservice performance and causing cascading failures.'\n\n#### 检查点：\n1. **关键错误类型和组件**:\n   - `adservice`服务在多个节点（包括`aiops-k8s-08`）上发生Java异常 (`Injected error`, `InvocationTargetException`)。\n   - 包含日志条目指出Node `aiops-k8s-08`上的`adservice-2` instance触发了一些异常行为。\n   \n2. **日志关键词检测**:\n   - 错误关键词包括 `rpc error`, `InvocationTargetException`, `Injected error`.\n   \n3. **关联上下游影响**:\n   - 从 `frontend`服务日志中发现大量 `failed to get ads: rpc error` 提示，明确指向`adservice`服务的调用失败。\n   - 这些失败可能由于`adservice`所在Node `aiops-k8s-08`的内存问题导致。\n\n### 输出验证结果 (JSON)\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"rpc error\", \"Unknown desc\", \"InvocationTargetException\", \"Injected error\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Java errors such as 'InvocationTargetException' and 'Injected error' occurred on adservice indicating possible malfunction due to environmental factors.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Logs from `adservice` show 'Exception in thread \\\"grpc-default-executor-170\\\" java.lang.Error: Injected error'.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"Recurrent 'failed to get ads: rpc error: code = Unknown desc' indicating that adservice was unable to handle requests.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Frontend logs indicate 'failed to retrieve ads' messages due to rpc error connecting with adservice.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n### 结论\n该分析支持初步假设，即 Node `aiops-k8s-08` 的内存不足对 `adservice` 服务性能产生了显著影响，并导致了一系列级联故障。建议进一步调查 Node 的内存使用情况，并检查 `adservice` 的内存管理策略，以防止类似问题的再次发生。", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于提供的监控数据，我进行如下分析以验证根因假设。\n\n### 核心观测数据\n从异常指标和节点到Pod的映射数据中，可以提取以下要点：\n1. **Node 异常**:\n   - 节点 `aiops-k8s-08` 在时间段内 `node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes` 降低了 13.86%（从 13.2GB 降至约 11.5GB），表明该节点可能出现了明显的内存压力。\n   - 无其他 `node_*` 指标（例如 CPU 或文件系统）显示异常，这表明问题可能集中在内存消耗。\n\n2. **影响范围**:\n   - 根据节点到Pod的映射关系，`aiops-k8s-08` 上运行了以下 Pods:\n     - `recommendationservice-0`\n     - `paymentservice-0`\n     - `productcatalogservice-2`\n     - `cartservice-2`\n     - `redis-cart-0`\n     - `adservice-2`\n   - 异常指标中，运行在 `aiops-k8s-08` 上的 `adservice-2` 显示 `rrt_max`有重要变化（0.56变化率，90秒）。`rrt`也显著升高。`redis-cart-0`的指标显示轻微 CPU 动态。\n\n3. **服务级异常**:\n   - Adservice的 `rrt_max` 是变化率最高的服务性能指标（0.56）。其延迟表现与在 `aiops-k8s-08` 上的Pod存在关联。\n   - 延迟指标和 Trace分析表明 `frontend -> adservice`服务链路延迟恶化。\n\n---\n\n### 核心验证与归类判断\n初步假设认为是Node `aiops-k8s-08`的内存耗尽问题导致了链路性能问题，而数据分析确实表明:\n1. `node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes` 是唯一直接显示异常的 `node_*` 参数。\n2. 在故障期间，多个服务受到延迟影响最显著的是 `adservice`运行在该节点上的Pod（`adservice-2`）。\n3. 其他系统级异常，如跨服务链路延迟，符合根因级联影响的模式。\n\n---\n\n### JSON化输出\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes\", \"rrt_max\", \"rrt\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-08\",\n      \"reason\": \"node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes下降13.86%，触发运行在该节点上的Pod（包括 adservice-2）性能恶化，导致 frontend->adservice 链路延迟升高。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"故障时间段内指标显示 node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes 从 13.2GB 降至 11.5GB；adservice 的 rrt_max 显著变化，Change Ratio 达 0.56。\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "trace_analysis_findings": "通过当前的调用链数据分析，我们可以进一步评估根因假设：\n\n### 分析结果\n1. **延迟指标分析**\n   - 检测到 `redis` 在 `aiops-k8s-08` 节点运行的两个操作——`HMSET` 和 `HGET` 的延迟显著上升，正常情况下耗时分别为大约 1361 ms 和 1553 ms，异常情况下耗时分别达到 15267 ms 和 9458 ms，分别增加了 >10 倍和约 6 倍。\n   - `cartservice` 的 `POST /GetCart` 和 `POST /EmptyCart` 在异常期间耗时也大幅增加，分别从正常 2556 ms 上升到异常 12886 ms（约 5 倍）和从正常 2307 ms 上升到异常 82071 ms（约 35 倍）。\n\n2. **错误状态分析**\n   - `frontend->adservice` 连续报错，状态码为 2，次数非常频繁，表明调用连接可能中断或转发失败。\n   - 主要错误集中于 `adservice` 的调用链，支持 `adservice` 出现严重性能问题的假设。\n\n### 根因定位判断\n1. **节点异常影响辨识**\n   - 数据显示，在 `aiops-k8s-08` 节点上运行的服务，如 `redis` 和 `cartservice`，在异常时间段内有显著延迟波动。\n   - `redis` 的操作耗时在异常期间出现了巨大攀升，与 `node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes` 的下降（基于 Metric 专家提供的信息）有潜在关联。\n\n2. **服务异常影响分析**\n   - 前端与 `adservice` 的调用反复报错，而 `adservice` 的性能下降也与 `frontend` 的调用链中显著延迟吻合。\n   - 依据调用拓扑，`adservice` 的故障直接影响到前端服务请求的处理。\n\n### 结论\n基于以上分析，当前根因假设：\"Node aiops-k8s-08 memory exhaustion is the root cause, impacting adservice performance and causing cascading failures.\" 得到验证支持。\n\n### 输出结论 (JSON)\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"latency_spike\",\n    \"frontend->adservice\",\n    \"cartservice->redis\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-08 (Node)\",\n      \"reason\": \"Detected significant latency spike in redis operations `HMSET` and `HGET`, occurring on aiops-k8s-08.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"HMSET normal: 1361 ms, anomaly: 15267 ms. HGET normal: 1553 ms, anomaly: 9458 ms.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Consistent failure in adservice call chain (`frontend->adservice`) leading to unresponsive or delayed requests.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Repeated status code 2 errors with frequent occurrences in frontend->adservice calls.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```"}
